WEBVTT

00:10:28.655 --> 00:10:30.214
to do things for them.

00:10:31.769 --> 00:10:37.712
Now, while the natural parenting instinct
is to comfort and protect

00:10:37.736 --> 00:10:39.112
and reassure kids,

00:10:40.207 --> 00:10:44.383
in 1930, the psychiatrist Alfred Adler

00:10:44.407 --> 00:10:46.706
had already cautioned parents

00:10:46.730 --> 00:10:49.770
that we can love a child
as much as we wish,

00:10:49.794 --> 00:10:52.196
but we must not make that child dependent.

00:10:52.838 --> 00:10:57.123
He advised parents to begin training kids
from the very beginning

00:10:57.147 --> 00:10:59.192
to stand on their own two feet.

